title: The Ronettes
description:
Just bought this album of Ebay. Have never been able to find a FLAC version out there, just mp3. Therefore I thought I would upload this one. Hope you enjoy it.

I've included the .log from Exact Audio Copy. It says that 3 tracks could be verified as accurate and the rest returned different results. Actually never had it before that only a couple of the tracks could be verified. Most of the times it's either the entire album or none. Don't know what that is about. I repeated the process and got the same results. 

Can only seed at night, but I will stick to it as long as there is interest or until there are enough seeders.
